Package edu.ntnu.idatt1002.backend.budgeting

Class Expenses

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt1002.backend.budgeting.Expenses
public class Expenses extends Object
A class that represents a collection of expenses. The collection of expenses is a HashMap with the expense name as key and the expense amount as value.
Version:
1.2 - 26.04.2023
Author:
Emil J., Vegard J., Sander S. and Elias T.
